Identify and measure the mobilisation factors
Instead, the operational revolution necessary for the smooth functioning of modern enterprises requires the adoption of a definitive view of human behavior.
It consists in integrating a basic protocol into every management consideration or practice: for the recipients, the commitment to the company is only possible if it clearly appears to be a means to realize part of their dreams, ambitions and projects.
