How much should you earn on your Facebook profile?
Facebook users can now find out what they should be earning based on their profile thanks to the new application Trovit, the search engine with the most ads for real estate, job offers and cars in Spain.
The "How much should you earn?" tool calculates users' salaries based on the more than 140,000 job offers available at Trovit in Spain.
